node.text: Pup: “you smell like fishe look like spidey” Crab: “well bish what kind of seal is you! Ol squish face lookin a$$ boy! Grunting when you breathe too like a pregnant woman at a buffet lookin a$$!” Dog: “that was not berry nice” Crab: “my bad ugly seal I sustained childhood trauma when a jelly fish attacked me which make me highly defensive it was just a defense technique 😟” Dog: “it’s ok I forgib” *crab nips dog’s face with claw* Dog: “why you hurted me” Crab: “another defensive mechanism I’m sorry I can’t control who I am I’m just a crab in a bucket 🥺” Dog: “come wif me my hooman adop you and you Lib in a lorge Tupperware and we feed you and you enjoy lorge suburban home with creature comforts like home theatre and neighborhood kids come pet you” Crab: “sounds amazing but it’s salt life for me homie I can’t give up the life of hot water, sunshine, sand, and b00ty cheeks I’m out ugly seal! It been real doe!” Dog: “ok water fren maybe another time ☺️” THE END BLESS UP 🙂😂😂
